OL,6,FResource bids from Stormont ministers
OL,7,Ffor money to alleviate pressures on
OL,8,Fpublic services in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Famount to more than three times the
OL,10,Ffunding available to Finance Minister
OL,11,FCaoimhe Archibald in the forthcoming
OL,12,Fbudget.JStormont's Finance Committee
OL,13,Fwas told Ms Archibald has received
OL,14,Fbids totalling #3.2billion for funding
OL,15,Ffrom her resource budget, but has only
OL,16,F#1 billion to allocate once previously
OL,17,Fearmarked funding is taken into
OL,18,Faccount.JFirst Minister Michelle
OL,19,FO'Neill has predicted that no
OL,20,Fministers will be happy when the
OL,21,Fbudget is set later this month, while
OL,22,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,23,FPengelly said difficult decisions
OL,24,Fwould have to be made.
